---
// Values section
---

<section id="values">
  <div class="section-container">
    <p class="section-label reveal">Beliefs</p>
    <h2 class="section-title reveal">How I work</h2>

    <div class="values-grid">
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <h3>Safety first</h3>
        <p>Diverse teams that feel safe produce better work. That's not ideology, it's what
          I've seen over and over.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3>Learn in the open</h3>
        <p>Share what you know. Share what you don't. Writing and teaching
          builds trust faster than having all the answers.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3>Ship early</h3>
        <p>Real feedback from real users beats any amount of planning.
          The best version is never the first one.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal">
        <h3>Unblock others</h3>
        <p>A manager's job is to make the team better, not to be the bottleneck.
          Coach, share context, get out of the way.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <h3>Keep it simple</h3>
        <p>The best architecture is the one the whole team understands.
          Maintainability beats cleverness.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="value-card reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <h3>Impact over credit</h3>
        <p>Good ideas can come from anywhere. What matters is
          building something useful, not who gets the credit.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
